---
title: Szechuan Pork & Green Bean Stir-Fry Lightning Prep
description: Forget takeout: the path to sweet-spicy-savory dinner bliss is as simple as breaking out a frying pan! In this recipe, ground pork and green beans are coated in tantalizing szechuan sauce and peanuts are transformed into the perfect crunchy topping thanks to a sugary coating. Everything comes together over a bed of steamy rice mixed with warm, sizzly ginger—in 30 minutes, no less! The results? A symphony of flavors and textures that are so delicious, you might just lick the plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e839d87cbbb135b3c4e9a66-45d2ab77.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/szechuan-pork-green-bean-stir-fry-5e839d87cbbb135b3c4e9a66-5d3bf28f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/szechuan-pork-green-bean-stir-fry-5e839d87cbbb135b3c4e9a66
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
course: main course
cuisine: Chinese
nutrition:
  calories: 770 kcal
